{"id":135239,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/02/简讯：烟花爆竹致北京近400死伤/","date":"2011-02-09T08:50:37Z","modified":"2011-02-09T08:50:37Z","title":"简讯：烟花爆竹致北京近400死伤","content":"<div>\n<p>北京市今年春节共有两人因燃放烟花爆竹死亡，388人受伤。</p>\n<p>另外截至星期一（2月7日）午夜，烟花爆竹还在北京造成194次火灾。</p>\n<p>北京在2006年恢复允许居民在春节燃放烟花爆竹。</p>\n<p>官员警告说，正月15将是另一个烟花爆竹燃放高峰。</p>\n<p>中央电视台新址就是在2009年春节的正月15因违禁燃放烟花而发生火灾。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/9L1VOSXJXA84OvlhTOp6wABvVxM/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/9L1VOSXJXA84OvlhTOp6wABvVxM/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/9L1VOSXJXA84OvlhTOp6wABvVxM/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/9L1VOSXJXA84OvlhTOp6wABvVxM/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=xKl-aeFHWgo:TfRT5DnJX1o:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=xKl-aeFHWgo:TfRT5DnJX1o:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=xKl-aeFHWgo:TfRT5DnJX1o:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=xKl-aeFHWgo:TfRT5DnJX1o:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=xKl-aeFHWgo:TfRT5DnJX1o:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=xKl-aeFHWgo:TfRT5DnJX1o:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/xKl-aeFHWgo\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>更多翻墙方式请发电邮(最好用Gmail)到:fanqiangyakexi1AT